  • Method Details

    • importBambda

      BambdaImportResult importBambda(String script)
      This method can be used to import a Bambda. It will overwrite any existing Bambda in the library with the same ID if the script imports without errors.
      Parameters:
      script - the Bambda script to import
      Returns:
      The BambdaImportResult which contains the result of importing the Bambda.
